Package: cfbscrapR
Title: A Scraping and Aggregating interface to the collegefootballdata.com API 
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: c(person('Saiem', 'Gilani', email = 'saiem.gilani@gmail.com', role = c('aut','cre')),
             person('Meyappan', 'Subbaiah', email = 'meysubb@gmail.com', role = c('aut')),
             person('Parker', 'Fleming', email = 'parkerf@smu.edu', role = c('aut')))
Description: An R package for working with College Football Data. It is an R API wrapper around https://collegefootballdata.com/ made available by cfbscrapR team. It provides users the capability to get a plethora of endpoints, and supplement that data with additional information (Expected Points Added/Win Probability added).
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
